Meri zindagi ka safar tha thoda mushkil,  
Doston ki baaton mein tha kuch toh khauf, sach ki thodi,  
Har pal tha tanha, dil tha udaas,  
Mann tha pareshan, sab kuch tha bekaar.

Jab tha gham ka andhera, sab the door,  
Dil tha yeh chahta tha, mil jaye kuch aur,  
Jitni bar maine koshish ki, utna hi tha gham,  
Doston ne chhoda tha, akele tha main num,  

Dil mein tha khali pan, na thi koi dua,  
Meri mehnat, meri soch, tha sab kuch guroor,  
Mujhe mila na pyaar, na tha koi sath,  
Phir bhi jiya tha, dil tha khud se waafa.

 
Noor ka tha safar mushkil, zindagi thi khali,  
Doston ne diya tha dard, lekin kuch ne bola,  
Jo thha safar ka hisaab, aaj wo sab tha fail,  
Par Noor ne dekha, jo tha har pal, wahi jeet gaya!

 
Jab takraayi zindagi, har mod pe tha ruk,  
Par Noor ne jaana, manzil bas uske haath ki thi chhup,  
Doston ne diya tha dard, tha sab kuch hi bhool,  
Par Noor ne dekha apne iradon mein thi taqat ki jhooth!

Aaj dekho, jahan tha kal wo tha kehna,  
Noor ki zindagi badli, badal gaya jeena,  
Mushkilon se ladke, sab ko dikhaya hai,  
Meri mehnat ka rang, waqt ne samjhaaya hai!

 
Noor ka tha safar mushkil, zindagi thi khali,  
Doston ne diya tha dard, lekin kuch ne bola,  
Jo thha safar ka hisaab, aaj wo sab tha fail,  
Par Noor ne dekha, jo tha har pal, wahi jeet gaya!

 
Zindagi mein kabhi na rukna, bas chalna hai,  
Jo nahi samjhe, unhein apni raah dikhani hai,  
Dost tha jab saath, ab hai apne dum,  
Noor ne paaya jo tha sab kuch, ab hai wo apne saath.
